Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.00,翻译人员专属 - 片尾（左上角）,,0,0,0,,翻译：@隐秀_（seriouszyx）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:05.08,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,We can generalize this idea of keeping things simple, using the term invariant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:05.08,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,我们可以用“不变量”这个术语来概括这个简化事情的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.83,0:00:10.66,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,So an invariant is simply a condition that is guaranteed to be true while your code is running,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.83,0:00:10.66,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,不变量只是一个在你的代码运行时被保证为真的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.66,0:00:12.08,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,assuming you haven't messed something up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.66,0:00:12.08,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,如果你没有搞砸什么的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.37,0:00:15.60,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,So it's the list of all the things that you can rely on-- all the truths.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.37,0:00:15.60,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,这些是你可以依赖的所有事实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.97,0:00:19.40,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,So an SLList with a sentinel node has at least the following invariants--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.97,0:00:19.40,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,具有哨兵节点的 SLList 至少具有以下不变量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:21.64,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,it has more, but here's a few that are kind of interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:21.64,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,其实有更多，但这几点很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:24.80,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,One is that the sentinel variable-- the sentinel reference--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:24.80,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,一个是 sentinel 变量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.81,0:00:26.65,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,it always points to a sentinel node.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.81,0:00:26.65,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,它总是指向哨兵节点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.65,0:00:30.04,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,That's something you have that's guaranteed to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.65,0:00:30.04,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,这是保证为真的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:35.21,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,Another is that the first node in the list, if it exists, is always at sentinel.next.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:35.21,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,另一种情况是 List 中的第一个节点（如果存在）总是位于 sentinel.next
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.80,0:00:40.51,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,And in fact, this is an invariant that I explicitly wrote out in the code right here as a comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.80,0:00:40.51,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,事实上，这个不变量我在代码中作为注释显式地写出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.16,0:00:47.41,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,Another one is that the size variable is always the total number of items that have been added, in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.16,0:00:47.41,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,另一点是 size 变量始终是已添加项的数量的总和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:49.66,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,And so what invariants are good for
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:49.66,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,不变量的好处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.66,0:00:53.17,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,is it make it easier to reason about your code.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.66,0:00:53.17,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,是更容易对你的代码推理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.47,0:00:56.11,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,You want to write a method that does something like, say, addLast?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.47,0:00:56.11,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,你想要编写一个类似于 addLast 的方法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.35,0:00:57.87,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,Well, you know all of these facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.35,0:00:57.87,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,你知道所有这些事实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.08,0:01:04.25,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,So you know, for example, that addLast doesn't need to-- uh oh-- to worry now-- to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.08,0:01:04.25,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,比如 addLast 现在不需要...去担心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:07.38,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,It don't have to worry about nulls--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:07.38,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,它不必担心空值
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.11,0:01:09.85,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,a null value at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.11,0:01:09.85,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,即 first 为 null
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.41,0:01:13.99,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,And it's also nice because it gives you a checklist of things you can think about,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.41,0:01:13.99,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,还有一点好处是它给了你需要考虑的检查清单
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.59,0:01:16.60,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,that once your method is finished running,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.59,0:01:16.60,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,一旦你的方法运行完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:18.24,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,all your invariants should be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:18.24,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,你所有的不变量都应该是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:21.69,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,So for example, when we're trying to write addFirst,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:21.69,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,例如，当我们尝试编写 addFirst 时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.95,0:01:24.51,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,well, we need to-- if we keep all those invariants in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.95,0:01:24.51,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,我们需要把所有这些不变量都牢记在心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.76,0:01:30.14,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,it might help avoid bugs like this, if we're-- if we have them listed on a sheet of paper or who knows what.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.76,0:01:30.14,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,如果把它们列在一张纸上，可能有助于避免这样的 bug
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.91,0:01:35.05,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,Now, some programmers actually do like writing out the invariants, having them in the code,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.91,0:01:35.05,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,一些程序员确实喜欢写出不变量，把它们放在代码中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:38.36,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,maybe even explicitly stating them as comments throughout.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:38.36,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,甚至可能从头到尾都明确地把它们写成注释
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.68,0:01:40.90,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,And sometimes you just think about them implicitly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.68,0:01:40.90,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,有时你只是隐约地想着它们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.90,0:01:42.47,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,But I hope that you'll find the notion useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.90,0:01:42.47,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,但我希望你会发现这个想法很有用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.28,0:01:44.51,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,So that's it for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.28,0:01:44.51,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,今天就到这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.51,0:01:46.96,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,In the next lecture, we're going to go even deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.51,0:01:46.96,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,在下一节课中，我们将更加深入
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:51.25,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,We're going to fix a couple of limitations of the SLList that we've come up with so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:51.25,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,我们将解决目前为止提出的 SLList 的几个限制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.64,0:01:53.92,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,For example, so far, we can only hold integers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.64,0:01:53.92,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,例如，到目前为止，我们只能保存整数
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.29,0:01:56.65,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,And if we look at addLast method, it's kind of slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.29,0:01:56.65,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,而且 addLast 方法有点慢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:01:58.75,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,So we're going to tackle those two problems next time,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:01:58.75,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,所以我们下次要解决这两个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.75,0:02:02.76,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,and then we'll talk a little bit about an alternate way to build lists, which is based on a raise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.75,0:02:02.76,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,然后稍微谈一谈建立链表的另一种方式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.02,0:02:03.86,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,So I'll see you then,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.02,0:02:03.86,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,到时见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:10.02,en - 白色,,0,0,0,,and I hope you found this tour into the weird world of sentinel nodes to be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:10.02,zh - 黄色,,0,0,0,,我希望你觉得这次进入哨兵节点的奇怪世界的旅行很有趣
